question.title: ANR keyDispatchingTimedOut but no own classes in stacktrace

node.contents: I receive bug reports for my Android-App regarding an ANR keyDispatchingTimedOut. Amazingly the stack traces within this report do not contain any of my own classes.

astNode.text: I receive bug reports for my Android-App regarding an ANR keyDispatchingTimedOut. Amazingly the stack traces within this report do not contain any of my own classes.

node.contents: I also checked my onPause() and onResume() methods, they should not need a very long time. There just some cleanup of resources is done, for onPause() I'd expect a worst-case-maximum of 1 second (but cause completely by things that have to be done, elsewhere I'd create a memory leak.
